《復仇者聯盟：無限之戰》收獲了評論家以及普羅大眾的普遍積極評論，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據488條評論，持有85%的新鮮度，平均得分7.6／10，該網站共識寫道：「《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》巧妙地嘲諷一群令人眼花繚亂的漫威電影宇宙英雄，以應對他們最嚴重的威脅，結果是一場驚心-{}-動魄，情緒共鳴的大片（大部分）實現了其巨大的野心。」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/avengers_infinity_war |title=Avengers: Infinity War (2018) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2018-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427004733/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/avengers_infinity_war |archive-date=2018-04-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了68分，代表「普遍正面好評」的評價<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/avengers-infinity-war |title=Avengers: Infinity War reviews |publisher=[[CBS|CBS]] |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2018-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117034655/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/avengers-infinity-war |archive-date=2018-01-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「A」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/avengers-infinity-war-second-weekend-box-office-overboard-tully-bad-samaritan-1202382713/|title=‘Avengers: Infinity War’ Is Second-Fastest Pic To $400M With Second-Best Weekend Ever At $115M+|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|publisher=[[Penske_Business_Media|Penske Business Media]]|date=2018-05-04|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|accessdate=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507140752/http://deadline.com/2018/05/avengers-infinity-war-second-weekend-box-office-overboard-tully-bad-samaritan-1202382713/|archive-date=2018-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

